<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
</head>

<body>
    <canvas id="canvas"></canvas>
    <div id="preloader">
        <div class="half-placeholder"></div>
        <div id="upper-half"></div>
        <div id="progress-bar-wrapper">
            <div class="progress-bar-placeholder"></div>
            <div id="progress-bar"></div>
            <div class="progress-bar-placeholder"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="lower-half"></div>
        <div class="half-placeholder"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="wrapper">

        <div id="headline-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <h1>Hello,<br />
                I'm Tim,<br />
                Freelance Developer.<br />
            </h1>
            <p id="subtitle"><span>web frontend</span><span>3D</span><span>android</span></p>
            <div class="message-buttons">
                <button class="message-button animated" data-animation="message" tabindex="1">get in touch</button>
                <button class="linkedin-button animated" data-animation="linkedin" tabindex="2"><i
                        class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>connect on
                    LinkedIn</button>
            </div>
            <a class="animated" id="about-button" data-animation="about" tabindex="3" href="#"><i
                    class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-right"></i><span>learn
                    more</span></a>
        </div>
        <div id="message-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <div>
                <a class="back-arrow" data-animation="headline" tabindex="1" href="#"><i
                        class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-left"></i></a>
            </div>
            <div id="message-form-wrapper">
                <h2>Let's have a chat.</h2>
                <form novalidate>
                    <div class="field-wrapper">
                        <span>
                            <input placeholder="Name" name="name" tabindex="2" autocomplete="on" id="name-input" />
                            <span></span>
                            <input placeholder="Email" name="emailaddress" type="email" tabindex="3" autocomplete="on"
                                id="emailaddress-input" />
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper">
                        <input placeholder="Subject" name="subject" autocomplete="off" tabindex="4"
                            id="subject-input" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper" id="textarea-wrapper">
                        <textarea placeholder="Message" name="message" autocomplete="off" tabindex="5"
                            id="message-input"></textarea>

                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper" id="submit-button-wrapper">
                        <button id="send-button" type="submit" tabindex="6"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="field-wrapper hide" id="invalid-input-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        <p>Please fill out all the fields.</p>
                    </div>
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Phone" name="phone" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no" type="tel" />
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no"
                        type="url" />
                    <input class="honey" placeholder="Email" name="email" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="no"
                        type="email" />
                </form>
                <div id="message-confirmation">
                    <div id="message-success">
                        <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        <h3>Thank you for your message.</h3>
                        <p>I'll get back to you as soon as possible!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-client-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                        <h3>400 (Bad Request)</h3>
                        <p>The server has rejected the data you entered.<br />Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the
                            inconvenience.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-server-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo-alt"></i>
                        <h3>400 (Internal Server Error)</h3>
                        <p>Uh. Oh. Something went wrong.<br />Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the inconvenience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message-unknown-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-redo-alt"></i>
                        <h3>Uh. Oh. Something went wrong.</h3>
                        <p>Please try again later.<br />Sorry for the inconvenience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="about-wrapper" class="section-wrapper">
            <div>
                <a class="back-arrow" data-animation="headline" tabindex="1" href="#"><i
                        class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-left"></i></a>
            </div>
            <div id="about-content">
                <h2>Tim Konieczny.</h2>
                <p lang="en">
                    My main areas of expertise are <b>font end development</b>, <b>computer graphics</b> and <b>digital
                        experiences</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    I specialize in small and medium web applications in <b>React / Redux</b> and <b>HTML / CSS</b>, and
                    in
                    creating <b>compelling user experiences</b> through <b>animations</b> and <b>transitions</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    Also, I’m passionate about <b>all things 3D</b>, and love working with <b>WebGL / three.js</b>, toy
                    around
                    with <b>shaders</b> and <b>Virtual Reality</b> tech like <b>WebXR</b>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    I also have experience building <b>native Android apps</b>, including <b>UI-driven-</b> and
                    <b>computer
                        graphics applications</b> (OpenGL ES).
                </p>
                <p lang="en">
                    <b>I’m always excited to tackle interesting projects and collaborate with great people. Sounds good?
                        Let’s
                        have a chat!</b>
                </p>
                <div class="message-buttons">
                    <button class="message-button" data-animation="message" tabindex="2">
                        get in touch
                    </button>
                    <button class="linkedin-button" data-animation="linkedin" tabindex="3">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>connect on LinkedIn
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>